					  "description": "CUET Results 2025 Live Updates: The National Testing Agency (NTA) has confirmed the release date for CUET-UG 2025 results. As lakhs of students await their scores, the results are declared today, July 4 on cuet.nta.nic.in.",
					  "keywords" : ["cuet","ceut result 2025 live","cuet ug result 2025 live","cuet result","cuet.nta.nic.in","cuet.nta.nic.in result","cuet.nta.nic.in 2025","nta cuet result","cuet result 2025","cuet ug result 2025","cuet ug","cuet ug results 2025 date","cuet ug result date 2025","nta","cuet ug result","cuet ug 2025 result","cuet result date 2025","nta cuet","cuet nta nic in","nta cuet ug result 2025","cuet ug 2025 result date","cuet ug results 2025","cuet nta","cuet. nta. nic. in","cuet result 2025 live updates","cuet result 2025 live","cuet result live","cuet ug result scorecard","cuet ug result link","cuet ug 2025","cuet 2025 result"],
					  "datePublished": "2025-07-04T07:42:00+05:30",
					  "dateModified": "2025-07-04T17:52:00+05:30",
					  
					  "articleSection" : "News",
					  "articleBody" : "The National Testing Agency (NTA) announced the CUET UG 2025 results today, July 4. Approximately 13.5 lakh candidates who appeared for the Common University Entrance Test for Undergraduate programmes can access their results on the official website — cuet.nta.nic.in. The CUET UG 2025 exam was conducted between May 13 and June 4 for admission into various central and participating universities. Once the results are declared, participating institutions will use the CUET UG scorecards to prepare their own merit lists. Some universities may also hold individual counselling sessions for admissions. For papers held in multiple shifts, candidates' raw scores will be normalized into NTA scores, which will serve as the final evaluation metric. These scores are valid only for admissions in the 2025–26 academic year.",
