/div><div id="breakingNews"><div class="contentwrapper prel"><ul class="bnews flt"></ul><div class="nextPrev"><span class="flt prev"></span><span class="flr next"></span></div></div></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="clearfix main_container"><section id="pageContent"><div class="live_update_blog"><div class="flt layout2"><div class="live_head"><div class="live live_stock"><i class="lb-icon slide"></i> LIVE BLOG</div></div><div class="textDiv l1"><h1>CUET UG Result 2025 Live: NTA releases result at cuet.nta.nic.in; check steps to download scorecards, answer key, toppers list and more </h1><span class="time">04 Jul 2025 | 05:52:41 PM IST</span><div class="share dtShare"><span class="flr lbShare lSprit"></span></div><div class="lsocial_links flt100 hide"><a aria-label="facebook" class="fb lSprit" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="Facebook#Share#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms#/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms" data-src="https://ecoti.in/N24EVZ" data-share-url="https://ecoti.in/N24EVZ" data-share-title="" title="facebook"></a><a class="wa lSprit" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="Whatsapp#Share#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms#/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms" data-src="https://ecoti.in/IUfdeY" data-share-url="https://ecoti.in/IUfdeY" data-watext="Hey, This might interest you! %0A%0A" data-share-title="" aria-label="whatsapp" title="whatsapp"></a><a aria-label="linkedin" class="in lSprit" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="LinkedIn#Share#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms#/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms" data-src="https://ecoti.in/OPqoWY" data-share-url="https://ecoti.in/OPqoWY" data-share-title="" title="linkedin"></a><a class="twt lSprit" href="javascript://" rel="nofollow" data-dimension="1" data-ga-onshare="Twitter#Tweet#https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms#/news/newsblogs/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list/liveblog/122238810.cms" data-src="https://ecoti.in/k2Rola" data-share-url="https://ecoti.in/k2Rola" data-share-title="" aria-label="twitter" title="twitter"></a><a class="lSprit closeShare" href="javascript://"></a></div></div><div class="transCont clearfix"><div class="imgDiv"><figure class="dib tac"><img alt="" height="181" width="243" fetchpriority="high" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-122238810,width-630,resizemode-4,imgsize-67825/cuet-ug-results-2025-live-updates-nta-cuet-ug-result-scorecard-download-direct-link-cuet-nta-nic-in-merit-list-pdf-download-toppers-list.jpg"></figure><div class="imgCaps">NTA CUET Result cuet.nta.nic Live Updates</div></div></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="smallCaps"><div class="smTxt">Synopsis</div><p>CUET Results 2025 Live Updates: The National Testing Agency (NTA) has confirmed the release date for CUET-UG 2025 results. As lakhs of students await their scores, the results are declared  today, July 4 on cuet.nta.nic.in. </p></div></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="prel lb_synop"><div data-length="857" class="lbSyn short_synop">The National Testing Agency (NTA) announced the CUET UG 2025 results today, July 4. Approximately 13.5 lakh candidates who appeared for the Common University Entrance Test for Undergraduate programmes can access their results on the official website — cuet.nta.nic.in.<br /><br />The CUET UG 2025 exam was conducted between May 13 and June 4 for admission into various central and participating universities.<br /><br />Once the results are declared, participating institutions will use the CUET UG scorecards to prepare their own merit lists. Some universities may also hold individual counselling sessions for admissions.<br /><br />For papers held in multiple shifts, candidates' raw scores will be normalized into NTA scores, which will serve as the final evaluation metric. These scores are valid only for admissions in the 2025–26 academic year.<br /></div><span class="read_more"> Show more</span><span class="read_less hidden"> Show less</span></div><div class="clr"></div><div id="updateBox"><div id="updateInfo" data-count="27" data-latCount="27"><b>1 New Update</b><span class="lSprit refresh"></span></div></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="pageliveblog" id="contentBox" style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:10px"><div class="clearfix container hitDone" data-page="1"><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122250821"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>05:52:18 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h2 class="">CUET UG Result 2025 Live: One candidate scores 100 percentile in four subjects, 17 bag top score in three subjects</h2><div class="blogSysn">CUET UG Result 2025 Live: One candidate has scored 100 percentile in four subjects in the Common Entrance University Test-Under Graduate (CUET-UG), while 17 candidates from across the country have bagged the top score in three subjects, the National Testing Agency (NTA) on Friday announced.<br />The NTA conducted CUET-UG in computer-based test (CBT) mode for 13,54,699 candidates. These candidates applied for various combinations of subjects for the academic session 2025-2026.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122246347"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>02:32:07 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Website down </h3><figure><img class="lazy gwt-Image" width="445" src="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-42031747,width-445,resizemode-4/etlogo.jpg" data-original="https://img.etimg.com/thumb/msid-122246347,width-445,resizemode-4,imgsize-5693/cuet-result-2025-live-updates-website-down-.jpg" alt="CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Website down "></figure></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div data-taboola="taboola_1"><div data-placement="Mid Category Thumbnails Live Blog" data-target_type="mix" data-mode="thumbnails-300x250" style="margin:0 auto;text-align:center;margin-bottom:12px;height:250px;" id="taboola-mid-category-thumbnails-2" loc="all" class="wdt-taboola adsbg300"></div></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122245859"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>02:08:51 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Steps to check</h3><div class="blogSysn">Visit the official website: cuet.nta.nic.in or nta.ac.in<br /><br />Click on the link that says “CUET UG 2025 Result” or “Download Scorecard”<br /><br />Enter your credentials – Application Number, Roll Number, and Date of Birth<br /><br />Submit the details to view your result<br /><br />Download and print your scorecard for future admission processes<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Ask ChatGPT<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122245663"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>01:59:41 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: CUET UG 2025 results declared, direct link activated</h3><div class="blogSysn">The CUET UG 2025 results have been officially announced by the National Testing Agency (NTA). Candidates can now access their scorecards via the active direct link at examinationservices.nic.in. Over 13 lakh students can log in using their application number and date of birth to view their results.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122245268"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>01:40:52 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Merit list and counselling</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Participating universities, institutes, or organizations will prepare a merit list. Based on the CUET (UG) 2025 scorecard issued by the NTA, universities may conduct their own counselling processes.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122243387"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>12:18:43 PM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Highest and lowest state applicants</h3><div class="blogSysn">According to the analytics released by the NTA for the CUET UG 2024 results announced on July 28, Uttar Pradesh recorded the highest number of applicants. In total, 3,47,736 students registered, and 2,96,858 appeared for the exam. Delhi followed as the second-highest, with 1,56,412 registrations and 1,37,145 students appearing for CUET UG admissions.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122242706"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>11:46:24 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Scheme</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: The CUET UG 2025 exam covered a total of 37 subjects, comprising 13 Indian languages, 23 domain-specific subjects, and one General Aptitude Test. Candidates could select up to five test papers, regardless of their Class 12 subject combinations.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div style="margin:0 auto; text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;" data-oop="0" data-size="[[300, 250]]" class="adsbg300 scroll_div" id="div-gpt-ad-158892319009749-2-122238810" data-adsSlot="/7176/Economictimes/ET_Liveblog/ET_Liveblog_Mid_1"></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122242464"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>11:34:51 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: What was the duration of the test?</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Each CUET UG 2025 test paper was held for a duration of 60 minutes and conducted across multiple shifts. PwBD candidates were provided with an additional 20 minutes of compensatory time for every hour of the exam.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122242071"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>11:14:23 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Eligibility criteria to appear for the exam</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Candidates who have either passed their Class 12 or equivalent examination or are appearing in 2025 are eligible to apply for CUET (UG). However, they must also meet the age requirements (if any) set by the specific university, institution, or organization where they wish to seek admission.<br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br />Ask ChatGPT<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122241861"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>11:02:07 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: How to check scores once declared?</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Once declared, the CUET result can be accessed from the official websites — nta.ac.in and cuet.nta.nic.in. To view their results, candidates need to log in using their application number and date of birth on the mentioned portals.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122241431"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:41:35 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: When and where to check CUET UG 2025 result?</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: As per the official update from the NTA, the CUET UG 2025 result will be released on July 4, though the exact time of release is yet to be confirmed. Once announced, the result will be available on the official websites. Along with the scorecards, the NTA will also publish subject-wise statistics and the total number of candidates who appeared and qualified.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122241296"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:34:02 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Who will prepare the merit list?</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: The merit list will be created by the participating universities, institutes, or organisations using the CUET UG 2025 scores. Based on these scores, each university may also hold its own counselling process for admission to undergraduate programmes.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div style="margin:0 auto; text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;" data-oop="0" data-size="[[300, 250]]" class="adsbg300 scroll_div" id="div-gpt-ad-1632979702261-2-122238810" data-adsSlot="/7176/Economictimes/ET_Liveblog/ET_Liveblog_Mid_2"></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122241100"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:24:03 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Steps to check the results</h3><div class="blogSysn">Step 1: Go to cuet.nta.nic.in<br /><br />Step 2: Click on the CUET UG 2025 result download link<br /><br />Step 3: On the next window, insert the roll number and registration number<br /><br />Step 4: Submit and download the CUET UG result 2025<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122241037"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:20:39 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: When were the results announced in past?</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET UG Result Date 2025: July 4<br /><br />CUET UG Result Date 2024: July 28<br /><br />CUET UG Result Date 2023: July 15<br /><br />CUET UG Result Date 2022: September 15<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122240816"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:07:45 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Official websites to check</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: The official websites to check and download the CUET UG 2025 scorecard are nta.ac.in and cuet.nta.nic.in.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122240754"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:04:20 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Marking scheme</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Correct answer: +5<br /><br />– Incorrect answer: – 1<br /><br />– Unanswered/ un-attempted: 0<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122240710"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>10:01:26 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: When and where to download CUET UG 2025 result</h3><div class="blogSysn">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Once declared, the CUET UG 2025 result will be accessible on the official websites — cuet.nta.nic.in and nta.ac.in. To view their results, candidates need to visit either site and log in using their application number and date of birth.</div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div style="margin:0 auto; text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;" data-oop="0" data-size="[[300, 250]]" class="adsbg300 scroll_div" id="div-gpt-ad-1632979718003-2-122238810" data-adsSlot="/7176/Economictimes/ET_Liveblog/ET_Liveblog_Mid_3"></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122240098"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>09:16:13 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET Result 2025 Live Updates: Will there re-evaluation of announced results?</h3><div class="blogSysn">The NTA has clarified that the result will not be re-evaluated/re-checked, and no correspondence in this regard will be entertained.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122239848"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>09:00:10 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: What login credentials will I need?</h3><div class="blogSysn">To log in, students will need: <br /><ul><li>CUET UG application number</li><li>Date of birth</li></ul></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122239604"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>08:42:06 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: How many students appeared last year?</h3><div class="blogSysn">A total of 13,47,618 students registered for CUET UG last year. Of them, as many as 7.17 lakh were male candidates, 6.30 lakh were female candidates and seven were transgender students.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122239447"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>08:29:26 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: Is there any negative marking?</h3><div class="blogSysn">Yes, there is negative marking in CUET evaluation. A mark will be deducted for each incorrect response.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122239204"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>08:10:41 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: List of Deemed Universities using CUET scores</h3><div class="blogSysn"><ul><li>Aurora Higher Education and Research Academy</li><li>Avinashilingam Institute for Home Science and Higher Education for Women</li><li>Dayalbagh Educational Institute</li><li>GITAM (Visakhapatnam)</li><li>GITAM (Bengaluru)</li><li>GITAM (Hyderabad)</li><li>Gokhale Institute of Politics and Economics</li><li>Graphic Era (Deemed to be University)</li><li>Gujarat Vidyapith</li><li>Gurukula Kangri</li><li>ICFAI (Hyderabad)</li><li>IIS (Deemed to be University), Jaipur</li><li>Jamia Hamdard</li><li>Jaypee Institute of Information Technology</li><li>Lakshmibai National Institute of Physical Education</li><li>Lingaya's Vidyapeeth</li><li>Maharishi Markandeshwar (Deemed to be University), Mullana - Ambala</li><li>Manav Rachna International Institute of Research and Studies</li><li>Nehru Gram Bharati (Deemed to be University)</li><li>Shobhit Institute of Engineering and Technology</li><li>SRM Institute of Science and Technology (Deemed University), NCR Campus</li><li>Tata Institute of Social Sciences (TISS)</li><li>TERI School of Advanced Studies</li><li>The Gandhigram Rural Institute (Deemed to be University)</li><li>Vinayaka Mission's Research Foundation</li></ul></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div style="margin:0 auto; text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;" data-oop="0" data-size="[[300, 250]]" class="adsbg300 scroll_div" id="div-gpt-ad-16329797180031-21-122238810" data-adsSlot="/7176/Economictimes/ET_Liveblog/ET_Liveblog_Mid_4"></div><div class="clr"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122238902"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>07:52:53 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: How to download CUET-UG scorecard</h3><div class="blogSysn"><ol><li>Visit the official NTA CUET website</li><li>Click on the link for CUET UG 2025 result</li><li>Enter your application number and date of birth</li><li>Submit the login details</li><li>The scorecard will appear on the screen</li><li>Verify all details and download the PDF for future use</li></ol></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122238895"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>07:52:11 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: Provisional and Final answer keys</h3><div class="blogSysn">The provisional answer key for CUET-UG 2025 was released by the National Testing Agency (NTA) June 15. Candidates were given a limited window till June 20 to raise objections and submit supporting documents for any disputed answers.<br /><br />Following the review of all challenges, the final answer key was published on July 1, 2025. This final version is used for calculating results and cannot be challenged further.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122238877"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>07:49:37 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: Minimum marks required to qualify in CUET-UG 2025</h3><div class="blogSysn">Candidates who score between 350 and 400 marks out of a total of 800 are generally considered as having qualified in the CUET-UG exam. However, qualifying does not guarantee admission, as each participating university sets its own cut-offs and eligibility criteria for various courses.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122238866"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>07:48:37 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: Where to check CUET UG scores?</h3><div class="blogSysn">Students can check their CUET UG results on its official website cuet.nta.nic.in.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div class="eachStory" id="lbn122238859"><div class="updateText"><div class="shareTime"><div class="timeStamp"><span class="bod"></span><span>07:47:36 AM IST, 04 Jul 2025</span></div></div><h3 class="">CUET 2025 Results Scorecard Live: Result date is out</h3><div class="blogSysn">The National Testing Agency had, earlier this week, announced that CUET UG 2025 result will be declared on July 4.<br /></div></div><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="lastbord"></div><div style="margin:0 auto; text-align:center;margin-bottom:10px;" data-oop="0" data-size="[[300, 250]]" class="adsbg300 scroll_div" id="div-gpt-ad-16329797180032-22-122238810" data-adsSlot="/7176/Economictimes/ET_Liveblog/ET_Liveblog_Mid_5"></div><div class="clr"></div></div></div><noscript><div class="clr"></div><div class="pagination1"><div class="pageno"><em class="active">1</em> </div></div></noscript><div class="clr"></div><div class="clearfix relatedTopics"><b>Read more on</b><span class="readanchore"><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore1"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore2"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>ceut result 2025 live</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore3"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet ug result 2025 live</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore4"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet result</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore5"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet.nta.nic.in</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore6"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet.nta.nic.in result</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore7"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet.nta.nic.in 2025</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore8"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>nta cuet result</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore9"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet result 2025</div><div class="rdMrBulDiv" data-track="ReadMore10"><span class="bulletGrey"></span>cuet ug result 2025</div></span></div><div id="defaultCommentForm" style="margin-left:0"><form method="post" class="cmtForm" id="commentOnArticle0" name="commentOnArticle0"><div class="subhead">Have something to say? <b>Post your comment</b></div><p class="cmtInfo">Comments are moderated and will be allowed if they are about the topic and not abusive.</p><textarea onkeyup="remainingChar(this,'atrcharcount0')" name="cmtMsg" placeholder="Your comment"></textarea><p class="cmtInfo">Characters remaining (<span id="atrcharcount0">1500</span>)</p><div class="hidden nonLogged"><h3>To post this comment you must</h3><div class="loginBtns"><p class="flt">Log In/Connect with:</p><a onclick="window.open('https://jsso.indiatimes.com/sso/identity/login/socialLogin?channel=et&amp;oauthsiteid=facebook','jsso','width=600,height=600');" href="javascript:void(0)" class="flt shareSprite fbLogin"></a><a onclick="window.open('https://jsso.indiatimes.com/sso/identity/login/socialLogin?channel=et&amp;oauthsiteid=googleplus','jsso','width=600,height=600');" href="javascript:void(0)" class="flt shareSprite gpLogin"></a><a onclick="sso.login(); window.scroll(0,0); return false;" class="moreLoginOpt flt" href="#">Indiatimes Network</a><div class="clr"></div></div></div><div class="uInfo hidden"><div class="or hidden nonLogged"><b>or</b></div><div><h3 class="hidden nonLogged">Fill in your details:</h3><label class="flt hidden nonLogged"><input name="fromname" maxlength="20" value="" placeholder="Name" type="text"><span>Will be displayed</span></label><label class="flt hidden nonLogged"><input name="fromaddress" maxlength="40" value="" placeholder="Email" type="text"><span>Will not be displayed</span></label><label style="margin:0" class="flt hidden nonLogged"><input id="location" name="location" maxlength="20" value="" placeholder="Location" type="text"><span>Will be displayed</span></label><div class="clr"></div></div><div class="shareCmt"><h3>Share this Comment:</h3><label><input name="chktwt" value="0" type="checkbox">Post to Twitter <img loading="lazy" src="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/photo/5552760.cms" alt="Twitter"></label><div class="clr"></div><h6>Please answer this simple math question.</h6><div class="flt"><span id="mathq0">3 + 1 =</span><input value="4" type="hidden" name="mathans" id="mathans0"></div><div class="flt"><input value="" name="mathuserans" id="mathuserans0" type="text"></div><div class="flt"><input type="submit" class="cmt_submit_btn" value="Post Comment"></div><div class="clr"></div></div></div><input value="1" id="roaltdetails" name="roaltdetails" type="hidden"><input id="id" name="id" type="hidden" value="122238810"><input value="0" id="parentid" name="parentid" type="hidden"><input value="0" id="rootid" name="rootid" type="hidden"></form><div class="hidden cmtMsg"></div></div><div id="cmtContainer" style="margin-left:0"></div><div data-url="/primebenefits_slider.cms?temp=Liveblog" class="lazyWidget clearfix rmfp skip_subscribed skip_expired_subscription"></div></div></section><aside id="sideBar"><style>
